            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英諾賽科與安森美半導體戰略合作 未來數年或帶來數億美元氮化鎵銷售",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英諾賽科(02577)公布，與納斯達克市場上市公司安森美半導體達成戰略合作，有望於未來數年帶數億美元的氮化鎵銷售。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：英諾賽科官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source-web_02577-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英諾賽科官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source-web_02577-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：英諾賽科官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今次戰略合作，旨在採用英諾賽科的8英寸硅基氮化鎵工藝，共同加速推進氮化鎵產業的應用和佈局。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">戰略合作將通過晶圓採購等方式，整合英諾賽科的氮化鎵製造能力，以及安森美半導體在系統封裝與集成等領域的經驗和優勢，加速推動氮化鎵在新能源汽車、人工智能、數據中心，工業等領域的快速落地。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15477601-%e8%8b%b1%e8%ab%be%e8%b3%bd%e7%a7%91%e8%88%87%e5%ae%89%e6%a3%ae%e7%be%8e%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%8e%e9%ab%94%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c-%e6%9c%aa%e4%be%86%e6%95%b8%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%96%e5%b8%b6%e4%be%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240613_FI_source-web_InnoScience-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-03 16:55:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "乘聯分會：11月全國乘用車新能源市場零售按年升7% 整體乘用車降7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘聯分會初步統計顯示，今年11月全國乘用車新能源市場零售135.4萬輛，按年增長7%，按月也升6%，滲透率升至59.8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250704_FI_source-ap_China_Automotive-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250704_FI_source-ap_China_Automotive-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內全國乘用車廠商新能源批發172萬輛，較去年同期增長20%，按月也升7%，滲透率57.5%。若將今年首11個月合計，全國乘用車新能源市場零售累計1150.4萬輛，按年升20%；累計批發1377.7萬輛，按年升29%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於全國整體乘用車市場零售方面，上月數字為226.3萬輛，按年減少7%，按月則升1%；今年累計零售2151.9萬輛，按年升6%。批發方面，11月數字為299.2萬輛，按年與按月均升2%，今年累計批發2676.6萬輛，較去年同期增加11%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15477572-%e4%b9%98%e8%81%af%e5%88%86%e6%9c%83%ef%bc%9a11%e6%9c%88%e5%85%a8%e5%9c%8b%e4%b9%98%e7%94%a8%e8%bb%8a%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%877",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250603_FI_source-ap_China_Automotive-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-03 16:50:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
