        {
            "title": "登場兩新股 樂摩科技高收36.25% 金岩高嶺新材收市僅高招股價2.19%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日掛牌兩隻新股均高開後升幅收窄，樂摩科技(02539)表現較佳，收報54.5元，較招股價40元高36.25%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"樂摩科技服務官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/Lemo-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"樂摩科技服務官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/Lemo-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">樂摩科技服務官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早高開62%，以64.8元開市，早市最高曾衝上78.65元，較招股價高96.63%，午後升幅顯著收窄，最低價49.3元時仍高於招股價23.25%；全日成交1.56億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以樂摩科技收市價54.5元及每手100股計，每認購及獲配1手股份賬面賺1450元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一隻今日掛牌的新股金岩高嶺新材(02693)，無論是股價與交投均相對遜色。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"金岩高嶺新材招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02693.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"金岩高嶺新材招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02693.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">金岩高嶺新材招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股高開逾27%後，初段曾見9.8元全日高位，較招股價7.3元高34.25%，但升幅迅速收窄，尾市更進一步試底，一度失守招股價，最低報7.25元；收報7.46元，較招股價只高2.19%，成交9960萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以該股1手500股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺80元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15477474-%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1-%e6%a8%82%e6%91%a9%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b636-25-%e9%87%91%e5%b2%a9%e9%ab%98%e5%b6%ba%e6%96%b0%e6%9d%90%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e5%83%85%e9%ab%98",
